-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e5d122d9-2b3e-4219-bd9b-cfccc50cdfb4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f72b3983-d599-4a24-9279-ea335f2bc93c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로봇 등이 여러 가지 모델링 기술로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-54478400-1630-4866-b425-745b9352b6e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d9698403-d571-49c0-b4be-786468d3d4dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만들어지기도 하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8e2fc352-fa88-4d05-bf8c-e87eec208da1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6278c1fc-52ee-4b84-9649-5fbcb29988b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단순하게는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cece94e8-0adc-4680-a870-9baa0c3f8e4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3f4a26c4-fe84-43bb-80e4-af0e6e193255\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의류 디자인 의상일 수도 있으며</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7c17e268-3f0c-4751-bbf9-7d2018dcc39e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a5a3bef9-4909-44af-860f-4569a937c67d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또는 책자 형태의 기록지 일 수도 있고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f6c368b0-f98d-46a7-85cb-f730e674668a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-074c4ed5-8cdc-477f-aab0-2ca10695bdeb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">조향 학과의 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1a5434d5-a8a3-4c45-bbdb-055a71fafe4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-48a3fdaa-7c63-4fc1-a2d6-ff5b96841cdb\" sty